===Mandarin===
*[[Pinyin]]: érhuà

===Noun===
# (''phonetic'') [[retroflex]] final "r". It has the character [[兒]], but is not a syllable.
#:*[[貓兒]] (māo ér) &mdash; [[cat]].
#:*[[花兒]] (huāér) &mdash; [[flower]].
#:*他[[火兒]]了 (tā huǒ ér le) &mdash; He got angry.

*ending in -i, -n: left out
*:一塊兒 yīkuàir &mdash; yīkuàr
*:慢慢兒 mànmàn ér &mdash; mànmàr
*:根兒 gēn ér &mdash; gēr

*ending in -ng: left out and nasalized
*:有空兒 yǒukòng ér &mdash; yǒukõr

